Why kolligate?
Why kolligate?
Get Paid More
kolligate allows you to set your hourly rates or send counter offers with the pay rate you desire
Rewards
Not only can you get paid from working shifts, but you have the opportunity to earn even more through the kolligate rewards program
Flexibility
kolligate lets you plan your work around your life as you have the option to choose when and where you work
Full Transparency
kolligate’s Discover feature allows you to explore available shifts that match your requirements
Easily Connect With Employers
You have the ability to connect with Job Posters and negotiate your own terms for shifts
Gain Experience
kolligate makes it simple to finish your certification process or get experience by connecting you with offices looking for externs or volunteers
